overview.en: The first decentralized community, the traffic portal in the blockchain world, external drainage, in-house education, and universal Internet scams help community members to fundamentally lift themselves out of poverty and realize wealth freedom.
overview.zh: 首个去中心化社区，区块链世界的流量入口，对外引流，对内教育，普及互联网骗局，帮助社区成员从根本上脱贫，实现财富自由。
